Package org.bonitasoft.engine.identity

Class UserUpdater

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bonitasoft.engine.identity.UserUpdater
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    public class UserUpdater
extends Object
implements Serializable
    represents a helper for updating a User. Chaining is possible with this updator to ease the User update.
    For instance, new UserUpdater.setUsername("john.doe").setFirstname("John").setLastname("Doe");
    Since:
    6.0.0
    Author:
    Matthieu Chaffotte, Celine Souchet
    See Also:
    User, Serialized Form
